## ğŸš€ Quick Start

### Prerequisites
- Node.js v16+
- MongoDB
- SambaNova API Key

### Installation
```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/harshal-soladhra/AI-Assistant.git

# Install server dependencies
cd server
npm install

# Install client dependencies
cd ../client
npm install
```

### Environment Setup

Create `server/.env`:
```env
MONGO_URI=your_monodb_uri
PORT=3000
JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret
SAMBANOVA_API_KEY=your_sambanova_api
```

### Run Application

**Terminal 1 - Backend:**
```bash
cd server
npm run dev
```

**Terminal 2 - Frontend:**
```bash
cd client
npm run dev
```

- Backend: `http://localhost:3000`
- Frontend: `http://localhost:5173`

## ğŸ“¡ API Endpoints

### Authentication
```http
POST   /api/auth/register        # Register a new user
POST   /api/auth/login           # Login user
GET    /api/auth/user            # Get logged-in user data (protected)
```

### AI Tutor
```http
GET     /api/conversations           # Get all conversations (protected)
POST    /api/conversations           # Create new conversation (protected)
PUT     /api/conversations/:id       # Update conversation title (protected)
DELETE  /api/conversations/:id       # Delete conversation (protected)


GET     /api/messages/:conversationId   # Get messages of a conversation (protected)
POST    /api/messages                   # Send user message (protected)
POST    /api/messages/chat              # AI chat response (protected)
    
```

### Courses
```http
GET    /api/data/service        # Get all available courses
POST   /api/user/enroll         # Enroll in a course (protected)
GET    /api/user/my-courses     # Get enrolled courses of logged-in user (protected)

```

### Contact
```http
POST   /api/form/contact      # Submit contact form
```

### Admin (Protected)

1= Users

```http
GET     /api/admin/users        # Get all users
PATCH   /api/admin/users/:id    # Update user by ID
DELETE  /api/admin/users/:id    # Delete user by ID

2= Contacts

GET     /api/admin/contacts     # Get all contact messages
DELETE  /api/admin/contacts/:id # Delete contact message

3=Services (Courses Management)

GET     /api/admin/services         # Get all services/courses
POST    /api/admin/services         # Create new service/course
PUT     /api/admin/services/:id     # Update service/course
DELETE  /api/admin/services/:id     # Delete service/course

4=Dashboard

GET     /api/admin/dashboard        # Get admin dashboard statistics


```


## ğŸ¤– AI Tutor Implementation

**Real AI Integration** -  Real-time, context-aware chat powered by SambaNova LLM  API  
**Conversation Storage** - MongoDB with full history  
**Context-Aware** - Maintains conversation context  
**Error Handling** - Fallback responses on API failure  
```javascript

// Example: Send message to AI
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "conversationId": "676f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d",
  "message": "Explain React hooks"
}
```

## ğŸ§ª Testing with Postman

1. **Login** to get JWT token
2. **Create conversation** - Copy the returned `conversationId`
3. **Send message** - Use the `conversationId` from step 2
4. **View history** - Get all conversations

